body.Value:
The following query to find the events:
CommonSecurityLog
| where TimeGenerated >= @{getPastTime(utcNow(), 'Hour', 4)} and TimeGenerated <= @{utcNow()}
| where SourceIp contains  @{first(body('Alert_-_Get_IPs')?['IPs'])}

